{"tid":2260431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"近百大陸抽砂船包圍台南竿島","createTime":"2020-10-27T14:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T03:03:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ee1f4cb819f627d245e7b087a73aa06663768468","tid":2260431,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201027/PLFKD3U24VFUTAEXIULLLWRTWQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201027%2FPLFKD3U24VFUTAEXIULLLWRTWQ%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=6a3f3cd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201027%2FPLFKD3U24VFUTAEXIULLLWRTWQ%2F&h=f6825b85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201027/PLFKD3U24VFUTAEXIULLLWRTWQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n近百大陸抽砂船包圍台南竿島<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ex65cwwz4fbZenL8s53jnW9WGLg=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FSBNPZ4BEJAIFL6D7ECLHQEGHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fex65cwwz4fbZenL8s53jnW9WGLg%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFSBNPZ4BEJAIFL6D7ECLHQEGHQ.jpg&h=98ebf685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■近百大陸抽砂船包圍南竿島。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n大陸抽砂船經常越界到台灣馬祖海域盜砂，。。。。。。。。。。。，100噸警艇毫無警示作用，海巡署相當重視。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台軍包機終抵東沙<br />\n<br />\n據報道，馬祖海巡隊當時已前往針對越界抽砂船進行驅離，但是這些抽砂船相當狡猾，全部圍繞在禁制水域線外圍，並不時侵入台方水域內。加上台灣警艇僅100噸大小，對於數百噸至上千噸重的抽砂船毫無警示作用。海艦隊分署特別派出西北艦前往支援，驅離了四艘運砂船及一艘抽砂船，目前大陸抽砂船均在限制水域外；另艦隊分署緊急調派新北艦全速趕往南竿海域。<br />\n<br />\n海巡署強調，。。。。。。。。。。。。，非屬管轄水域。<br />\n<br />\n台灣立榮航空軍用包機原定15日由高雄小港機場飛往東沙，但當時因香港區管中心拒絕進入，而被迫折返。到了上周四（22日）又因颱風原因取消，包機最終在昨天順利起飛，並於早上9時抵達東沙，補給物資與接載島上官兵返回台灣。台灣海洋委員會海巡署負責人沒有回應有否先跟香港方面聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"1425306a04e8856cc22fc532aaa6edd57e688ea2","tid":2260431,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:43:26.000Z","msg":"魚雷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cf3b3b6b0d5f2327ca59aa406134ce684677db","tid":2260431,"uid":27946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:46:33.000Z","msg":"小英：同我拉人封艇"},{"pid":"5a91296efe7aa7fc83c7cf6165df0973ba830b84","tid":2260431,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:47:47.000Z","msg":"銀牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72df05f8bb33cb28d3190365c5153755711e379","tid":2260431,"uid":196092,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:48:37.000Z","msg":"全部擊沉"},{"pid":"4906d76bc96bfa72bfce05b020aca4e24dcde955","tid":2260431,"uid":363413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2c7eac94d28483621238c91b34fc0c722024c0","tid":2260431,"uid":228955,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:05:14.000Z","msg":"打沉佢啦"},{"pid":"11c119ed374964919e96c4ab7afb6aefef583ac6","tid":2260431,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:09:10.000Z","msg":"直接擊沉啦"},{"pid":"99b763e700e4ccf3f1b372073d93d8923a5a2b49","tid":2260431,"uid":50526,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"試下美國嘅武器先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cf0cb8fde529f02ed0b406b1bd0111f98316b5","tid":2260431,"uid":107681,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T15:13:21.000Z","msg":"船盡沒官，人則正法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a958d18069425643a6e36f31f87d619027c6ab92","